      <section eId="sec_CHC-1244">
        <num>CHC 1244</num>
        <heading>1244. Â Consent of parent</heading>
        <subsection eId="CHC-1244__subsec_A">
          <num>A.</num>
          <content>
            <p>Except as otherwise provided herein, any parent may execute an authentic act consenting to the adoption of his child in an intrafamily adoption, including a waiver of service or notice for any subsequent proceeding.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CHC-1244__subsec_B">
          <num>B.</num>
          <content>
            <p>If the parent of a child born of marriage is married to the stepparent petitioner and executes an authentic act of consent, he need not join in the petition nor be served with a copy thereof.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CHC-1244__subsec_C">
          <num>C.</num>
          <content>
            <p>The parent of a child born outside of marriage who is married to the petitioning spouse shall join in the petition.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CHC-1244__subsec_D">
          <num>D.</num>
          <content>
            <p>Repealed by</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
